================================================================================
=                                    README                                    =
================================================================================

Functionality
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The purpose is to provide a method of control for the Pioneer 3DX model.

LEFT CLICK - Selects a location to move the robot over to.

H - Halts the movement of the robot.

O - Outputs the object's current position.

P - Outputs the location hovered over by the mouse.

ESC - Exits the program.



Starting the application
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Place desired image into the "images" folder within the package.

2. Rename the image "background.png".

3. Change the variables "WINDOW_WIDTH" and "WINDOW_WIDTH" to match the
	dimensions of the desired image.

2. Run the command:
	roslaunch position_publisher interface.launch